Articles.Content:
Simple, simple game that might be fun!

 

HOW TO PLAY: Simply take any forum game on here and make a parody of it! First list the actual game, then the parody title, and how you play said parody game.

- - - - - - - - - - - 

 

(parody of Make a wish... and have it corrupted!)

Make a Wish... And have it granted!

Poster 1 makes a wish, and poster 2 then grants the wish normally, and then posts a new wish.

Parody of Parody Forum Game. 

The poster takes a parody posted on this game, and makes a parody of it.

Edited February 18, 2016 by cubinator

Parody of [Parody of (Parody Forum Game)]

Takes a parody of a parody posted on the parody of the original parody game, and makes a parody of it.

Edited February 18, 2016 by Matuchkin

Parody of {Parody of [Parody of (Parody Forum Game)]}

Takes a parody of a parody posted on the parody of the parody of the parody of the original parody game, and makes a parody parody of it.
